d?doi=10.1.1.462.2056&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">\"A change detection experiment using vegetation indices\"</a>. <i>Photogrammetric Engineering and Remote Sensing</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">14 March</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Photogrammetric+Engineering+and+Remote+Sensing&amp;rft.atitle=A+change+detection+experiment+using+vegetation+indices&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.aulast=Lyon&amp;rft.aufirst=John+G&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fciteseerx.ist.psu.edu%2Fviewdoc%2Fdownload%3Fdoi%3D10.1.1.462.2056%26rep%3Drep1%26type%3Dpdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVegetation+Index\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-EklundhOlsson2003-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-EklundhOlsson2003_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Eklundh, L.; Olsson, L. (2003). \"Vegetation index trends for the African Sahel 1982-1999\". <i>Geophysical Research Letters</i>. <b>30</b> (8). <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1029/2002GL016772\">10.1029/2002GL016772</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0094-8276\">0094-8276</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Geophysical+Research+Letters&amp;rft.atitle=Vegetation+index+trends+for+the+African+Sahel+1982-1999&amp;rft.volume=30&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1029%2F2002GL016772&amp;rft.issn=00948276&amp;rft.aulast=Eklundh&amp;rft.aufirst=L.&amp;rft.au=Olsson%2C+L.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVegetation+Index\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-GilliesKustas1997-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-GilliesKustas1997_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Gillies, R. R.; Kustas, W. P.; Humes, K. S. (1997). \"A verification of the 'triangle' method for obtaining surface soil water content and energy fluxes from remote measurements of the Normalized Difference Vegetation Index (NDVI) and surface e\". <i>International Journal of Remote Sensing</i>. <b>18</b> (15): 3145\u20133166. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1080/014311697217026\">10.1080/014311697217026</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0143-1161\">0143-1161</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Journal+of+Remote+Sensing&amp;rft.atitle=A+verification+of+the+%27triangle%27+method+for+obtaining+surface+soil+water+content+and+energy+fluxes+from+remote+measurements+of+the+Normalized+Difference+Vegetation+Index+%28NDVI%29+and+surface+e&amp;rft.volume=18&amp;rft.issue=15&amp;rft.pages=3145-3166&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1080%2F014311697217026&amp;rft.issn=0143-1161&amp;rft.aulast=Gillies&amp;rft.aufirst=R.+R.&amp;rft.au=Kustas%2C+W.+P.&amp;rft.au=Humes%2C+K.+S.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVegetation+Index\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-SandholtRasmussen2002-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Sand